mailsend -to test@gmail.com -from test@gmail.com -starttls -port 587 -auth -smtp smtp.gmail.com -sub 'test' +cc +bc -v -user test@gmail.com -pass 'pass' -mime-type 'text/html' -msg-body /root/signalization_project/signalization_off.html

Input data:
 echo "22" > /sys/class/gpio/export
 echo "out" >/sys/class/gpio/gpio22/direction
 echo "0" > /sys/class/gpio/gpio22/value
 echo "1" > /sys/class/gpio/gpio22/value

Read port:
 cat /sys/class/gpio/gpio19/value
 cat /sys/class/gpio/gpio20/value
 cat /sys/class/gpio/gpio22/value

